# Use Clerk skills for auth

When working on authentication, sign-in/sign-up, middleware for auth, or Clerk-related code in this project, use the skills in `.cursor/skills/`:

- **clerk** — Router; start here for any Clerk/auth task so the right sub-skill is used.
- **clerk-setup** — Adding or configuring Clerk.
- **clerk-custom-ui** — Custom auth UI and appearance.
- **clerk-nextjs-patterns** — Next.js middleware, Server Actions, caching.

Read the relevant skill's SKILL.md and follow its instructions so implementation matches this project's setup.
